net.markenwerk.commons.collections.sinks

Interface Sink<Payload>

  • Type Parameters:
    Payload - The payload type
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractCollectionSink, AbstractHandlerSink, AbstractSequenceSink, AbstractSink, AbstractStackSink, CollectionSink, HandlerSink, SequenceSink, StackSink

    public interface Sink<Payload>
    A Sink is write-only data structure.

    A Sink is intended to be used in API interfaces where the publishing component wants to expose write-only access.

    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Torsten Krause (tk at markenwerk dot net)
